data.Name: hellocentral
data.Bio: Fueled by an ambitious, genre-spanning take on modern alternative rock, and energetic yet emotional live performances, hellocentral has taken the Denver music scene by storm over the past two years. Formed in late 2017 in Denver, CO by four life-long friends, hellocentral is the product of a culmination of influences, experiences, and a common passion for music.
